snippet.title: The Most Dangerous Building in Manhattan
snippet.description:
How a single phone call from a student helped uncover a flaw that nearly toppled Citicorp. Get an exclusive 15% discount on Saily data plans! Use code veritasium at checkout. Download Saily app or go to https://saily.com/veritasium 

If you’re looking for a molecular modeling kit, try Snatoms, a kit I invented where the atoms snap together magnetically - https://ve42.co/SnatomsV 

▀▀▀
0:00 Why is the citicorp building on stilts?
4:44 How wind load works
7:49 Tuned Mass Dampers 
11:17 The Anonymous Student
14:00 Quartering Winds
18:38 What were the odds of collapse?
20:31 How was the citicorp building fixed?
25:40 Hurricane Ella
27:00 TMDs Take Over The World
28:36 Conspiracies and Cover Ups

▀▀▀
A big thank you for the incredible people without whom we couldn't have done this! 🖤

To Michael Greenburg, author of The Great Miscalculation, for his insights that really brought the story and its context to life. He gave us a pre-copy of his upcoming book, and it is fantastic: https://ve42.co/Miscalc
To Eric Hines for all his help with the technical details, fact-checking, and making sure we got the engineering right.

To Michael J. Vardaro for helping us uncover the details of the story and the resources he provided. 
To Brock Hedegaard for helping us dive deep into the Citicorp structural analysis. Learn the fundamentals of structural analysis on his brilliant channel: https://www.youtube.com/@StructuresProfH/videos
To Michele Barbato from UC Davis for his inputs on the load calculations.
https://faculty.engineering.ucdavis.edu/barbato/

To Prof. Chris Letchford who helped us understand the impact of wind on Citicorp's structure. 
To DongHun Yeo from NIST for discussing his research about wind effects on buildings similar to citicorp: https://ve42.co/WindLoad

Finally, to Team Columbia —who built the epic TMD and ran wind tunnel experiments that made this story come alive.
This includes the folks at the Mechanical Engineering Teaching Laboratory
(Follow all the cool stuff they’re doing: @mechcu, @columbiaengineering or visit https://teachinglab.me/)
Amanda Lombardo, Manager of Instructional Laboratories
Daniela Durón García, Assistant Manager of Instructional Laboratories
Jorge Casas, Machinist
And the amazing seniors from the Columbia Space Initiative:
(Support their awesome work here: columbiaspace.org/support-us/, Follow them: @columbiaspaceinitiative)
Michael Sheehan
Claudio Solano
Jessica Bolar
Kathryn Lampo

▀▀▀
References:
Michael M. Greenburg. The Great Miscalculation via. nyupress.org - https://ve42.co/Miscalc
 Joe Morgenstern. The Fifty-Nine-Story Crisis via. The New Yorker - https://ve42.co/59Crisis
National Academy of Engineering. William LeMessurier-The Fifty-Nine-Story Crisis: A Lesson in Professional Behavior - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=um-7IlAdAtg
Diane Lee Hartley. Implications of a Major Urban Office Complex: The Scientific, Social and Symbolic Meanings of Citicorp Center via. princeton.edu - https://ve42.co/CitiSymbol
Caroline Whitbeck. William LeMessurier: The Fifty-Nine-Story Crisis, A Lesson in Professional Behavior via.  Online Ethics - https://ve42.co/BillCrisis
Eugene Kremer. (Re)examining the Citicorp Case: ethical paragon or chimera? via. cambridge.org - https://ve42.co/EthicStorm
Project SERENE, Lemessurier Associates
Addition References here: https://ve42.co/citiref

▀▀▀
Special thanks to our Patreon supporters:
Adam Foreman, Albert Wenger, Alex Porter, Alexander Tamas, Anton Ragin, Autodidactic Studios, Balkrishna Heroor, Bertrand Serlet, Blake Byers, Bruce, Dave Kircher, David Johnston, David Tseng, Evgeny Skvortsov, Garrett Mueller, Gnare, gpoly, Greg Scopel, HydrochloRick, Jon Jamison, Juan Benet, Keith England, KeyWestr, Kyi, Lee Redden, Marinus Kuivenhoven, Matthias Wrobel, Meekay, meg noah, Michael Krugman, Orlando Bassotto, Paul Peijzel, Richard Sundvall, Sam Lutfi, Tj Steyn, TTST, Ubiquity Ventures, wolfee

27:00 TMDs Take Over The World
28:36 Conspiracies and Cover Ups

▀▀▀
A big thank you for the incredible people without whom we couldn't have done this! 🖤

To Michael Greenburg, author of The Great Miscalculation, for his insights that really brought the story and its context to life. He gave us a pre-copy of his upcoming book, and it is fantastic: https://ve42.co/Miscalc
To Eric Hines for all his help with the technical details, fact-checking, and making sure we got the engineering right.

To Michael J. Vardaro for helping us uncover the details of the story and the resources he provided. 
To Brock Hedegaard for helping us dive deep into the Citicorp structural analysis. Learn the fundamentals of structural analysis on his brilliant channel: https://www.youtube.com/@StructuresProfH/videos
To Michele Barbato from UC Davis for his inputs on the load calculations.
https://faculty.engineering.ucdavis.edu/barbato/

To Prof. Chris Letchford who helped us understand the impact of wind on Citicorp's structure. 
To DongHun Yeo from NIST for discussing his research about wind effects on buildings similar to citicorp: https://ve42.co/WindLoad

Finally, to Team Columbia —who built the epic TMD and ran wind tunnel experiments that made this story come alive.
This includes the folks at the Mechanical Engineering Teaching Laboratory
(Follow all the cool stuff they’re doing: @mechcu, @columbiaengineering or visit https://teachinglab.me/)
Amanda Lombardo, Manager of Instructional Laboratories
Daniela Durón García, Assistant Manager of Instructional Laboratories
Jorge Casas, Machinist
And the amazing seniors from the Columbia Space Initiative:
(Support their awesome work here: columbiaspace.org/support-us/, Follow them: @columbiaspaceinitiative)
Michael Sheehan
Claudio Solano
Jessica Bolar
Kathryn Lampo

snippet.description:

Disclaimer:
Maglock contains amorphous silica silicate, which differs significantly from crystalline silica associated with silicosis and other lung conditions. While amorphous silica is generally considered safe and rapidly dissolves if inhaled, prolonged inhalation of any dust particles should always be avoided. We recommend using Maglock responsibly: Minimize airborne dust, use in well-ventilated areas, and avoid deliberate inhalation.

id.title: Kompetisi terbaik saya dalam TAHUN-TAHUN
id.description:
Dapatkan MagLock Non-Chalk 8g GRATIS (penguat cengkeraman berbahan dasar silika) dengan pesanan apa pun di atas $100 USD. Gunakan kode FREEMAGLOCK ▶︎ https://rungne.com

Penafian:
Maglock mengandung silika silikat amorf, yang sangat berbeda dari silika kristal yang dikaitkan dengan silikosis dan kondisi paru-paru lainnya. Meskipun silika amorf umumnya dianggap aman dan cepat larut jika terhirup, menghirup partikel debu dalam waktu lama harus selalu dihindari. Kami sarankan untuk menggunakan Maglock secara bertanggung jawab: Minimalkan debu di udara, gunakan di area yang berventilasi baik, dan hindari menghirupnya secara sengaja.

Avvertenza:
Maglock contiene silicato di silice amorfa, che differisce significativamente dalla silice cristallina associata alla silicosi e ad altre patologie polmonari. Sebbene la silice amorfa sia generalmente considerata sicura e si dissolva rapidamente se inalata, l'inalazione prolungata di particelle di polvere dovrebbe sempre essere evitata. Consigliamo di utilizzare Maglock in modo responsabile: ridurre al minimo la polvere nell'aria, utilizzare in aree ben ventilate ed evitare l'inalazione intenzionale.

Haftungsausschluss:
Maglock enthält amorphes Silica-Silikat, das sich deutlich von kristallinem Silica unterscheidet, das mit Silikose und anderen Lungenerkrankungen in Verbindung gebracht wird. Amorphes Silica gilt zwar allgemein als sicher und löst sich beim Einatmen schnell auf, längeres Einatmen von Staubpartikeln sollte jedoch stets vermieden werden. Wir empfehlen einen verantwortungsvollen Umgang mit Maglock: Minimieren Sie Staub in der Luft, verwenden Sie es in gut belüfteten Bereichen und vermeiden Sie absichtliches Einatmen.

hi.description:
$100 USD से ज़्यादा के किसी भी ऑर्डर पर मुफ़्त 8g MagLock नॉन-चॉक (सिलिका-आधारित ग्रिप एन्हांसर) पाएँ। कोड FREEMAGLOCK का इस्तेमाल करें ▶︎ https://rungne.com

अस्वीकरण:
मैग्लॉक में अनाकार सिलिका सिलिकेट होता है, जो सिलिकोसिस और अन्य फेफड़ों की स्थितियों से जुड़े क्रिस्टलीय सिलिका से काफ़ी अलग होता है। जबकि अनाकार सिलिका को आम तौर पर सुरक्षित माना जाता है और साँस लेने पर तेज़ी से घुल जाता है, किसी भी धूल के कणों को लंबे समय तक साँस में लेने से हमेशा बचना चाहिए। हम मैगलॉक का ज़िम्मेदारी से इस्तेमाल करने की सलाह देते हैं: हवा में उड़ने वाली धूल को कम से कम करें, हवादार जगहों पर इस्तेमाल करें और जानबूझकर साँस में लेने से बचें।

snippet.title: I Connected My Three Giant Vivariums Together and It Changed Everything
snippet.description:
I finally connected my three giant ecosystem vivariums together, and the result was unbelievable. My long term plan had come to completion when my rainforest floor vivarium, canopy vivarium, and tropical wetlands vivarium became a single space, with shared animals freely able to cross over to the different habitats. I was shocked at what animals crossed over through the new cave tunnel bridge. Our rainforest ecosystem within glass has been forever changed. Hope you enjoy the Season 4 Finale of my Ecosystem Vivarium Series. Ant love forever! This video was shot in 4K Ultra HD resolution.

it.title: Ho collegato i miei tre terrari giganti e tutto è cambiato
it.description:
Ho finalmente collegato i miei tre giganteschi vivari ecosistemici e il risultato è stato incredibile. Il mio piano a lungo termine si è concluso quando il mio vivario sul suolo della foresta pluviale, il vivario sulla volta e il vivario delle zone umide tropicali sono diventati un unico spazio, con animali condivisi in grado di attraversare liberamente i diversi habitat. Sono rimasto scioccato da quali animali siano riusciti a passare attraverso il nuovo ponte a tunnel nella grotta. Il nostro ecosistema della foresta pluviale in vetro è cambiato per sempre. Spero che vi piaccia il finale della quarta stagione della mia serie "Vivarium Ecosistemici". Amore per le formiche per sempre! Questo video è stato girato in risoluzione 4K Ultra HD. id.title: Saya Menyambungkan Tiga Vivarium Raksasa Saya dan Itu Mengubah Segalanya
id.description:
Akhirnya saya menghubungkan tiga vivarium ekosistem raksasa saya bersama-sama, dan hasilnya sungguh luar biasa. Rencana jangka panjang saya telah selesai ketika vivarium lantai hutan hujan, vivarium kanopi, dan vivarium lahan basah tropis saya menjadi satu ruang, dengan hewan-hewan yang digunakan bersama dapat dengan bebas menyeberang ke habitat yang berbeda. Saya terkejut melihat hewan-hewan apa saja yang menyeberang melalui jembatan terowongan gua yang baru. Ekosistem hutan hujan kita di dalam kaca telah berubah selamanya. Semoga Anda menikmati Final Musim ke-4 dari Seri Vivarium Ekosistem saya. Cinta semut selamanya! Video ini direkam dalam resolusi 4K Ultra HD. de-DE.title: Ich habe meine drei riesigen Terrarien miteinander verbunden und das hat alles verändert
de-DE.description:
Ich habe endlich meine drei riesigen Ökosystem-Terrarien miteinander verbunden, und das Ergebnis war unglaublich. Mein langfristiger Plan war abgeschlossen, als mein Regenwald-Boden-Terrarien, mein Baumkronen-Terrarien und mein tropisches Feuchtgebiet-Terrarien zu einem einzigen Raum wurden, in dem die Tiere ungehindert in die verschiedenen Lebensräume wechseln konnten. Ich war schockiert, welche Tiere durch die neue Höhlentunnelbrücke kamen. Unser Regenwald-Ökosystem in Glas hat sich für immer verändert. Ich hoffe, euch gefällt das Finale der vierten Staffel meiner Ökosystem-Terrarien-Serie. Ameisenliebe für immer! Dieses Video wurde in 4K Ultra HD-Auflösung aufgenommen. fr-FR.title: J'ai connecté mes trois vivariums géants ensemble et cela a tout changé
fr-FR.description:
J'ai enfin relié mes trois vivariums géants d'écosystèmes, et le résultat est incroyable. Mon projet à long terme a été concrétisé lorsque mon vivarium de sol de forêt tropicale, mon vivarium de canopée et mon vivarium de zones humides tropicales sont devenus un seul espace, où les animaux communs pouvaient librement se déplacer d'un habitat à l'autre. J'ai été stupéfait de voir combien d'animaux traversaient le nouveau pont-tunnel de la grotte. Notre écosystème de forêt tropicale vitré a été transformé à jamais. J'espère que vous apprécierez le dernier épisode de la saison 4 de ma série sur les vivariums d'écosystèmes. Amour éternel pour les fourmis ! Cette vidéo a été tournée en résolution 4K Ultra HD.

en.title: I Connected My Three Giant Vivariums Together and It Changed Everything
en.description:
I finally connected my three giant ecosystem vivariums together, and the result was unbelievable. My long term plan had come to completion when my rainforest floor vivarium, canopy vivarium, and tropical wetlands vivarium became a single space, with shared animals freely able to cross over to the different habitats. I was shocked at what animals crossed over through the new cave tunnel bridge. Our rainforest ecosystem within glass has been forever changed. Hope you enjoy the Season 4 Finale of my Ecosystem Vivarium Series. Ant love forever! This video was shot in 4K Ultra HD resolution.

pt-BR.title: Conectei meus três vivários gigantes e isso mudou tudo
pt-BR.description:
Finalmente conectei meus três viveiros gigantes de ecossistemas, e o resultado foi inacreditável. Meu plano de longo prazo foi concluído quando meu viveiro de piso de floresta tropical, viveiro de copa e viveiro de áreas úmidas tropicais se tornaram um único espaço, com animais compartilhados podendo atravessar livremente para os diferentes habitats. Fiquei chocado com a quantidade de animais que atravessaram a nova ponte do túnel da caverna. Nosso ecossistema de floresta tropical dentro do vidro mudou para sempre. ja.title: 3つの巨大なビバリウムをつなげたらすべてが変わった
ja.description:
ついに3つの巨大なエコシステムビバリウムを繋げることができ、信じられないほど素晴らしい結果が得られました。熱帯雨林の床面、キャノピー、そして熱帯湿地のビバリウムが一つの空間となり、共有していた動物たちが自由に異なる生息地へ行き来できるようになった時、長年の計画がついに完成しました。新しい洞窟トンネルの橋を渡ってきた動物たちの姿には、本当に驚きました。ガラスの中にある私たちの熱帯雨林のエコシステムは、永遠に変わりました。エコシステムビバリウムシリーズ、シーズン4のフィナーレをお楽しみください。アリの愛よ、永遠なれ！この動画は4K Ultra HD解像度で撮影されました。

hi.title: मैंने अपने तीन विशाल विवरियम को एक साथ जोड़ दिया और इसने सब कुछ बदल दिया
hi.description:
मैंने आखिरकार अपने तीन विशाल पारिस्थितिकी तंत्र विवरियम को एक साथ जोड़ दिया, और परिणाम अविश्वसनीय था। मेरी दीर्घकालिक योजना तब पूरी हुई जब मेरा वर्षावन तल विवरियम, चंदवा विवरियम, और उष्णकटिबंधीय आर्द्रभूमि विवरियम एक ही स्थान बन गया, जिसमें साझा जानवर स्वतंत्र रूप से विभिन्न आवासों में पार करने में सक्षम थे। मैं हैरान था कि नए गुफा सुरंग पुल के माध्यम से कौन से जानवर पार हो गए। कांच के भीतर हमारा वर्षावन पारिस्थितिकी तंत्र हमेशा के लिए बदल गया है। आशा है कि आप मेरी इकोसिस्टम विवरियम सीरीज़ के सीज़न 4 के समापन का आनंद लेंगे। चींटियों का प्यार हमेशा के लिए! यह वीडियो 4K अल्ट्रा एचडी रिज़ॉल्यूशन में शूट किया गया था। इस चैनल पर नए लाभ/मतदान शक्तियों तक पहुँच प्राप्त करने के लिए ग्रेट एसी सीनेट में शामिल हों:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCONd1SNf3_QqjzjCVsURNuA/join

es-US.title: Conecté mis tres viveros gigantes y cambió todo
es-US.description:
Finalmente conecté mis tres gigantescos viveros de ecosistemas, y el resultado fue increíble. Mi plan a largo plazo se materializó cuando mi vivero de suelo de selva tropical, mi vivero de dosel y mi vivero de humedales tropicales se convirtieron en un solo espacio, donde los animales compartidos podían cruzar libremente entre los diferentes hábitats. Me sorprendió la cantidad de animales que cruzaban por el nuevo puente-túnel de la cueva. Nuestro ecosistema de selva tropical dentro de un cristal ha cambiado para siempre. Espero que disfruten del final de la cuarta temporada de mi serie "Vivarios de Ecosistemas". ¡Amor de hormigas para siempre! Este video se grabó en resolución 4K Ultra HD.

snippet.title: Reaction to Shedeur Sanders drafted by Cleveland Browns in NFL Draft | Colin Cowherd Podcast
snippet.description:
Colin reacts to Shedeur Sanders' fall in the NFL draft and the Cleveland Browns finally drafting him in the 5th round. He explains why Shedeur isn’t a good enough prospect to overcome the circus surrounding him, why his father Deion’s hubris hurt his draft stock, and why NFL teams don’t want a “celebrity quarterback” as their backup.

Timeline
0:00 Deion’s hubris didn’t help Shedeur’s draft stock
2:00 Shedeur wasn’t a good enough prospect to be making demands of NFL teams
3:45 “Quarterback Dad” is becoming “Pageant Mom” and hurts the kid
5:00 Multiple teams reported that Shedeur was bad in meetings and not engaged
6:30 Maturity and focus matter more for quarterbacks
9:45 Cleveland’s quarterback room is a mess
11:15 Shedeur is a good, not great prospect
13:00 Teams don’t want a “celebrity QB” as their backup

fr-FR.title: Réaction à la sélection de Shedeur Sanders par les Browns de Cleveland lors de la draft NFL | Pod...
fr-FR.description:
Colin réagit à la défaite de Shedeur Sanders lors de la draft NFL et à sa sélection finale par les Browns de Cleveland au 5e tour. Il explique pourquoi Shedeur n'est pas un espoir suffisamment prometteur pour surmonter le cirque qui l'entoure, pourquoi l'orgueil de son père Deion a nui à sa popularité, et pourquoi les équipes NFL ne veulent pas d'un « quarterback célèbre » comme remplaçant. Chronologie
0:00 L'orgueil de Deion n'a pas aidé Shedeur à se qualifier pour la draft
2:00 Shedeur n'était pas un assez bon prospect pour avoir des exigences envers les équipes de la NFL
3:45 « Papa quarterback » devient « Maman concours » et nuit à l'enfant
5:00 Plusieurs équipes ont signalé que Shedeur était mauvais en réunion et peu impliqué
6:30 La maturité et la concentration sont plus importantes pour les quarterbacks
9:45 La salle des quarterbacks de Cleveland est un désastre
11:15 Shedeur est un bon prospect, mais pas un excellent prospect
13:00 Les équipes ne veulent pas d'un « quarterback célèbre » comme remplaçant

snippet.title: I Spent 24 Hours at the World's Largest Hotel
snippet.description:
Thanks to Saily for sponsoring this video!! Get an exclusive 15% discount on Saily data plans by using code “SAFIYA” at checkout. Download the Saily app or go to https://saily.com/safiya 🕺🏻

HELLO FRIENDS!! And welcome to another video!! For years, Tyler and I have dreamt about visiting the World’s Largest Hotel, located all the way in the Genting Highlands, Malaysia - and to conclude our trip to Southeast Asia last summer (where we pulled All-Nighter in Singapore, spent 24 hours at Singapore’s Changi Airport, and ate at the famed Malaysian night market Jalan Alor), we headed into the mountains to spend 24 hours at the First World Hotel.

From their indoor AND outdoor theme park(s), to their celebrity chef restaurants, scenic views, Ice Age roller coasters and questionable towels, it was certainly a whirlwind 24 hours. What did you guys think? Would you visit this hotel? And where should we go next?

es-US.description:

¡HOLA, AMIGOS! ¡Bienvenidos a otro video! Durante años, Tyler y yo soñamos con visitar el hotel más grande del mundo, ubicado en las Tierras Altas de Genting, Malasia. Para concluir nuestro viaje al Sudeste Asiático el verano pasado (donde hicimos noche en Singapur, pasamos 24 horas en el Aeropuerto Changi de Singapur y comimos en el famoso mercado nocturno malasio de Jalan Alor), nos dirigimos a las montañas para pasar 24 horas en el First World Hotel.

Desde sus parques temáticos interiores y exteriores, hasta sus restaurantes con chefs famosos, vistas panorámicas, montañas rusas de la Edad de Hielo y toallas de dudosa calidad, sin duda fueron 24 horas de locura. ¿Qué les pareció? ¿Visitarían este hotel? ¿Y adónde deberíamos ir después? it.title: Ho trascorso 24 ore nell'hotel più grande del mondo
it.description:
Grazie a Saily per aver sponsorizzato questo video!! Ottieni uno sconto esclusivo del 15% sui piani dati Saily utilizzando il codice "SAFIYA" al momento del pagamento. Scarica l'app Saily o visita https://saily.com/safiya 🕺🏻

CIAO AMICI!! E benvenuti a un altro video!! Per anni, io e Tyler abbiamo sognato di visitare l'hotel più grande del mondo, situato nelle Genting Highlands, in Malesia. E per concludere il nostro viaggio nel Sud-est asiatico la scorsa estate (dove abbiamo fatto una nottata a Singapore, trascorso 24 ore all'aeroporto di Changi e mangiato al famoso mercato notturno malese di Jalan Alor), ci siamo diretti in montagna per trascorrere 24 ore al First World Hotel.

Tra i parchi a tema interni ed esterni, i ristoranti con chef famosi, le viste panoramiche, le montagne russe in stile era glaciale e gli asciugamani discutibili, sono state sicuramente 24 ore da capogiro. Cosa ne pensate? Visitereste questo hotel? E dove dovremmo andare adesso?

de-DE.title: Ich habe 24 Stunden im größten Hotel der Welt verbracht
de-DE.description:
Vielen Dank an Saily für das Sponsoring dieses Videos! Sichert euch exklusiv 15 % Rabatt auf Saily-Datentarife mit dem Code „SAFIYA“ beim Bezahlen. Ladet die Saily-App herunter oder besucht https://saily.com/safiya 🕺🏻

HALLO FREUNDE! Und willkommen zu einem weiteren Video! Tyler und ich träumen schon seit Jahren davon, das größte Hotel der Welt zu besuchen, das mitten in den Genting Highlands in Malaysia liegt. Zum Abschluss unserer Südostasienreise im letzten Sommer (wo wir in Singapur die ganze Nacht durchgemacht, 24 Stunden am Flughafen Singapur Changi verbracht und auf dem berühmten malaysischen Nachtmarkt Jalan Alor gegessen haben) sind wir in die Berge gefahren, um 24 Stunden im First World Hotel zu verbringen.

Von den Indoor- und Outdoor-Freizeitparks über die Restaurants mit Starköchen, malerischen Aussichten, Eiszeit-Achterbahnen und fragwürdigen Handtüchern – es waren definitiv turbulente 24 Stunden. Was meint ihr? Würdet ihr dieses Hotel besuchen? Und wohin sollten wir als Nächstes gehen?

fr-FR.title: J'ai passé 24 heures dans le plus grand hôtel du monde
fr-FR.description:
Merci à Saily pour le sponsoring de cette vidéo ! Bénéficiez d'une réduction exclusive de 15 % sur vos forfaits de données Saily en utilisant le code « SAFIYA » lors du paiement. Téléchargez l'application Saily ou rendez-vous sur https://saily.com/safiya 🕺🏻

BONJOUR LES AMIS ! Et bienvenue dans cette nouvelle vidéo ! Depuis des années, Tyler et moi rêvons de visiter le plus grand hôtel du monde, situé au cœur des Genting Highlands, en Malaisie. Pour conclure notre voyage en Asie du Sud-Est l'été dernier (où nous avons passé une nuit blanche à Singapour, 24 heures à l'aéroport Changi de Singapour et un repas au célèbre marché nocturne malaisien Jalan Alor), nous avons pris la direction des montagnes pour passer 24 heures au First World Hotel.

De leurs parcs d'attractions intérieurs et extérieurs, à leurs restaurants de chefs célèbres, en passant par des vues panoramiques, des montagnes russes de l'Âge de Glace et des serviettes douteuses, ce furent 24 heures de folie. Qu'en avez-vous pensé ? Allez-vous visiter cet hôtel ? Et où devrions-nous aller ensuite ?

en.title: I Spent 24 Hours at the World's Largest Hotel
en.description:
Thanks to Saily for sponsoring this video!! Get an exclusive 15% discount on Saily data plans by using code “SAFIYA” at checkout. Download the Saily app or go to https://saily.com/safiya 🕺🏻

HELLO FRIENDS!! And welcome to another video!! For years, Tyler and I have dreamt about visiting the World’s Largest Hotel, located all the way in the Genting Highlands, Malaysia - and to conclude our trip to Southeast Asia last summer (where we pulled All-Nighter in Singapore, spent 24 hours at Singapore’s Changi Airport, and ate at the famed Malaysian night market Jalan Alor), we headed into the mountains to spend 24 hours at the First World Hotel.

From their indoor AND outdoor theme park(s), to their celebrity chef restaurants, scenic views, Ice Age roller coasters and questionable towels, it was certainly a whirlwind 24 hours. What did you guys think? Would you visit this hotel? And where should we go next?

id.title: Saya Menghabiskan 24 Jam di Hotel Terbesar di Dunia
id.description:

HALO TEMAN-TEMAN!! Dan selamat datang di video lainnya!! Selama bertahun-tahun, Tyler dan saya bermimpi untuk mengunjungi Hotel Terbesar di Dunia, yang terletak di Genting Highlands, Malaysia - dan untuk mengakhiri perjalanan kami ke Asia Tenggara musim panas lalu (di mana kami begadang semalaman di Singapura, menghabiskan 24 jam di Bandara Changi Singapura, dan makan di pasar malam Malaysia yang terkenal, Jalan Alor), kami menuju ke pegunungan untuk menghabiskan 24 jam di First World Hotel.

Dari taman hiburan dalam DAN luar ruangan, hingga restoran koki selebriti, pemandangan indah, roller coaster Ice Age, dan handuk yang meragukan, itu benar-benar 24 jam yang luar biasa. hi.title: मैंने दुनिया के सबसे बड़े होटल में 24 घंटे बिताए
hi.description:
इस वीडियो को प्रायोजित करने के लिए Saily का धन्यवाद!! चेकआउट के समय कोड “SAFIYA” का उपयोग करके Saily डेटा प्लान पर 15% की विशेष छूट प्राप्त करें। Saily ऐप डाउनलोड करें या https://saily.com/safiya पर जाएँ 🕺🏻

नमस्ते दोस्तों!! और एक और वीडियो में आपका स्वागत है!! सालों से, टायलर और मैं दुनिया के सबसे बड़े होटल में जाने का सपना देख रहे थे, जो मलेशिया के जेंटिंग हाइलैंड्स में स्थित है - और पिछली गर्मियों में दक्षिण-पूर्व एशिया की अपनी यात्रा को समाप्त करने के लिए (जहाँ हमने सिंगापुर में पूरी रात बिताई, सिंगापुर के चांगी हवाई अड्डे पर 24 घंटे बिताए, और प्रसिद्ध मलेशियाई नाइट मार्केट जालान अलोर में खाना खाया), हम फर्स्ट वर्ल्ड होटल में 24 घंटे बिताने के लिए पहाड़ों की ओर चल पड़े।

उनके इनडोर और आउटडोर थीम पार्क से लेकर उनके सेलिब्रिटी शेफ़ रेस्तराँ, सुंदर दृश्य, आइस एज रोलर कोस्टर और संदिग्ध तौलिये तक, यह निश्चित रूप से 24 घंटे एक बवंडर की तरह थे। आप लोगों ने क्या सोचा? क्या आप इस होटल में जाएँगे? और हमें आगे कहाँ जाना चाहिए?

ja.title: 世界最大のホテルで24時間過ごしました
ja.description:
この動画をスポンサーしてくださったSailyに感謝します！ チェックアウト時にコード「SAFIYA」を入力すると、Sailyデータプランが15%オフになります。Sailyアプリをダウンロードするか、https://saily.com/safiya にアクセスしてください🕺🏻

皆さん、こんにちは！ また動画へようこそ！ タイラーと私は何年も前から、マレーシアのゲンティンハイランドにある世界最大のホテルを訪れることを夢見ていました。そして昨年の夏の東南アジア旅行（シンガポールで徹夜し、シンガポールのチャンギ空港で24時間過ごし、マレーシアの有名なナイトマーケット、ジャラン・アロールで食事をしました）の締めくくりに、山奥にあるファーストワールドホテルで24時間を過ごしました。

屋内と屋外のテーマパーク、有名シェフのレストラン、絶景、アイスエイジ風のジェットコースター、そしてちょっと怪しいタオルなど、まさに目まぐるしい24時間でした。皆さんはどう思いましたか？このホテルに泊まってみたいですか？次はどこへ行こうかな？

snippet.title: HELLAVERSE UPDATE
snippet.description:
GUESS WHAT?!! Helluva is comin' to Prime BUT it's also still going to be here too!! snippet.title: Exclusive: Young Thug Speaks on New Album and Life After Jail | The GQ Video Cover Story
snippet.description:
“I love people so much to the point that, the only thing that will make me not love you anymore is betrayal,” says Young Thug as he towers over _GQ’s_ Zach Baron in a perfectly landscaped garden, which sits next to an eccentric taxidermy-filled mansion on the East Side of Los Angeles.

In October of last year, the rapper Young Thug walked free from the Fulton County jail in Atlanta, concluding one of the strangest and most fraught spectacles in modern music. In May 2022 as part of a complex RICO case, Georgia prosecutors alleged that Young Thug—in addition to being the head of a record label, YSL—was also the leader of a gang of the same name. What followed was the longest criminal trial in Georgia history. 

Since getting out, Young Thug has mostly laid low, to the point of sometimes wearing a mask in public. He has not said much about the last few years of his life, or about anything at all, really… until now. This is the _GQ_ Video Covery Story with Young Thug.

----------

snippet.title: AMISTA 💔 (VIDEO OFICIAL) | BLESSD ❌ OVY ON THE DRUMS
snippet.description:
💔 AMISTA  |  BLESSD ❌ @OvyOnTheDrums 

Mira mis más recientes videos
TE CANTO BAJITO ▶️▶️ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4wcbJGoDvqM
ULTRA COMPLICADO REMIX ▶️▶️ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eeBQrWAVSV0

SUBSCRÍBETE  para ver mis nuevos videos aquí 
▶️ https://Blessd.lnk.to/BlessdYoutube

Sígueme en mis redes sociales:  
▶️ Instagram https://Blessd.lnk.to/Instagram
▶️ Facebook https://Blessd.lnk.to/Facebook

LETRA

Amista

Voy a ahogarme  con la realidad si no te digo esto,todavía te extraño,todavía te pienso,reina no te estoy hablando yo,son mis sentimientos,sé que tuve mis fallos ya he aprendido de ellos y a veces quiero pensar que tú tampoco a mí me has dejado de pensar lo que veo en tus redes es lo contrario,ver tus perfiles  es un mal necesario.

Y si me vieras quizás algo de ti de pronto a mi quisiera regresar reina yo no pierdo la esperanza de que algún día volvamos,ojalá sintieras esto que estoy sintiendo,ojalá y me vieras así bebiendo para que te des cuenta que por ti estoy muriendo  pero si no quieres volver entiendo.

Estoy tomando … para matar este guayabo amoroso de tanto hablarte ma creo que es acoso,tú fuiste la más linda aunque perdí lo más valioso quiero volverte a ver así suene ambicioso y sé que tú perdón no merezco,pienso en lo que hice y hasta yo me aborrezco si en tu vida  más no aparezco quiero que sepas que por todo te agradezco.

Te pienso mucho niña, extraño esos besitos con sabor a caipiriña,me muero de celos pensando que otro el ojo te guiña ojalá y no me olvides si con el tú te encariñas.

Ayer que regresé a mi pueblo alguien me dijo que ya te casaste,mírame y dime si ya me olvidaste bebé no te deseo el mal pero ojalá sintieras esto que estoy sintiendo,ojalá y me vieras así bebiendo para que te des cuenta que por ti estoy muriendo pero si no quieres volver entiendo.

#AMISTA

#Trap  
#Blessd

baby que es la que hay? (que lo que)
tienes jeva o tienes jevo? (ey)

no es confetti eso es cash
y eso q es petty namás
mami si te vas conmigo
tu espalda va contra el dash
lo hacemos encima del stash
el video con el flash
tu como que estas a switch
obligao que voy a smash

rich lifestyle
quieren ser mis baby mamas

snippet.title: #6 Tennessee vs #7 LSU (Doyle v Anderson, MUST WATCH, AMAZING GAME!) | 2025 College Baseball
snippet.description:
Tennessee Baseball and LSU Baseball opened up a top 10 ranked weekend series in the 2025 College Baseball Season.

Covering sports in a unique way since 2018. 

If you’re looking for high quality sports content, then this is the channel for you! I’ve covered Baseball (NCAA, LLWS, Professional), Football (NCAA, NFL), Softball (NCAA), Basketball (NBA, NCAA), Hockey (NHL), and much more!

The best part of my work as a YouTuber is being able to provide coverage of sports that may not receive as much attention as they should to the large audience I have built over the years. Many of the sports I cover aren't posted by any other YouTubers, which makes this channel that much more important.

One of my favorite accomplishments is revolutionizing the way sports channels create thumbnails. I've adopted two different styles, one with logos on the left and a game snapshot on the right, and the other with the logos in the middle and game snapshots representing both teams on either side.

I have a combined 4 years of experience as a Baseball & Basketball Play by Play announcer, which is where I learned my skills for commentary/breakdowns.

Twitter: @WheelsYT
Instagram: @wheels.yt
Email: wheels.partnerships@gmail.com

snippet.title: Donald Trump departs DC for Pope Francis' funeral aboard Air Force One with first lady Melania Trump
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump and first lady Melania Trump boarded Air Force One together at Joint Base Andrews in Maryland on Friday, April 25, 2025, to fly to Rome. The presidential couple will be attending the funeral processions in Vatican City for Pope Francis.

00:00 - Melania and Donald Trump arrive at Joint Base Andrews aboard Marine One
05:53 - Donald Trump boards Air Force One with Melania Trump
08:00 - Air Force One prepares to fly Melania and Donald Trump to Italy
11:51 - Melania and Donald Trump take off on Air Force One for Pope Francis funeral

snippet.title: John Stamos Hears Papa Roach For The First Time
snippet.description:
Take a sneak peek inside the mind of John Stamos – drummer for The Beach Boys! Watch as he listens to "Last Resort" by Papa Roach for the very first time—and attempts to play along. What is he listening for? How does he immediately craft an appropriate drum part? Tune in and find out!

John also gives a special thanks to @LudwigDrumsHQ and @ZildjianCompany!

snippet.description:
I rescued a barn-find 1970 Dodge Super Bee that was parked for 36 years! That means it was ignored since 1989. This is my second concurrent ’70 Super Bee, as I still own my first car that I bought in 1983. This new one is a 383 four-speed car. 

In the video, I’ll drag out the Bee and clean it up, you’ll see me score a ton of other parts, and I’ll even walk you through an amazing collection of vintage tractors and a machine shop from 1904!

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The director of Prey welcomes you to a world of hurt. Experience Predator: Badlands on the big screen, in theaters and IMAX November 7.
 
“Predator: Badlands,” which stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, is set in the future on a remote planet, where a young Predator (Schuster-Koloamatangi), outcast from his clan, finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Fanning) and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O’Connor.

localized.title: Predator: Badlands | Teaser Trailer
localized.description:
The director of Prey welcomes you to a world of hurt. Experience Predator: Badlands on the big screen, in theaters and IMAX November 7.
 
“Predator: Badlands,” which stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, is set in the future on a remote planet, where a young Predator (Schuster-Koloamatangi), outcast from his clan, finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Fanning) and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O’Connor.

snippet.title: Grupo Frontera: Tiny Desk Concert
snippet.description:
Anamaria Sayre | April 24, 2025
Grupo Frontera, which was headlining backyard bailes well before stadium shows, feels perfectly made for Tiny Desk. Beneath the glow of fluorescent office lights and backed against trinket-stuffed shelves, the match feels divinely ordained.

Normally, jazzy vocal trills and norteño cumbia rhythms are star-crossed lovers, but not at the Tiny Desk. At the center of a pop-infused reinvigoration of traditional Mexican sounds, the members of Grupo Frontera are masters of unlikely pairings. Mega-producer and songwriter Edgar Barrera discovered Grupo Frontera at a quinceanera in his hometown, enthralled by the band's authenticity. He encouraged the band's Texas-bred beats, killer melodies and contemporary lyrics.

There's no better space to highlight the impressive musicality of the group and stunning vocals of Payo Solis than in a stripped down setting. "Yo nací pa' querer a la que no me quiere (I was born to love the one who doesn't love me)," Payo coos. But it's hard to feel heartbroken when desamor sounds so smooth.

SET LIST
"un x100to"
"Hecha Pa' Mi"
"Ángel"
"Por Qué Será"
"EL AMOR DE SU VIDA"

MUSICIANS
Payo Solis: vocals
Juan Cantú: accordion
Julian Peña: congas, bongos
Beto Acosta: bajo quinto
Carlos Guerrero: drums
Daniel Uribe: pedal steel, guitar
Patricia Ligia: bass
Monty Rivera: keys, background vocals
Catherine "Cathia" Ochoa: background vocals
MJ Songstress: background vocals
Ella Bric: trumpet

TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Anamaria Sayre
Director: Joshua Bryant
Audio Technical Director: Josh Newell
Host/Series Producer: Bobby Carter
Video Editor: Maia Stern
Videographers: Joshua Bryant, Kara Frame, Maia Stern, Grace Raver
Audio Engineer: Josephine Nyounai
Production Assistants: Ashley Pointer, Dora Levite
Photographer: Michael Zamora
Tiny Desk Series Editor: Lars Gotrich
Executive Producer: Suraya Mohamed
Series Creators: Bob Boilen, Stephen Thompson
VP, Visuals and Music: Keith Jenkins

#nprmusic #tinydesk #grupofrontera

snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - Elena Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Bringing a pawsitive attitude and capoeira style, Elena charges in to Street Fighter 6 on June 5 as the final character from Year 2!

With a herd of fluid moves that will turn any opponent into prey, Elena promises each fight will be elephantastic.

Elena can be purchased individually with Fighter Coins and the owners of the Year 2 Character Pass / Ultimate Pass or Years 1-2 Fighters Edition, will automatically get access to Elena when she releases.

Please note that depending on the timezone you reside in, Elena may release the day before on June 4 following server maintenance.

https://streetfighter.com/6/

Please note that depending on the timezone you reside in, Elena may release the day before on June 4 following server maintenance.

snippet.title: Gruden’s QB Class | Jaxson Dart
snippet.description:
This episode of Gruden’s QB Class features University of Ole Miss quarterback Jaxson Dart. 

Gruden’s QB Class is hosted by Super Bowl-winning head coach Jon Gruden and showcases six of the quarterbacks heading into this year’s NFL draft. Gruden’s QB Class aims to explain football to the average fan while also putting the quarterbacks through a professional-style QB/Coach meeting and tackling on-field challenges that they will soon see in the NFL.

Gruden’s QB Class is proudly presented by Chevy. Explore Chevy Silverado at Chevy.com

snippet.title: A Video About Digging A Hole
snippet.description:
"Every kid in the world wants to dig a great big hole," said X-Ray. "To China, right?" | Watch all my exclusive videos by joining Nebula at https://go.nebula.tv/jacob-geller

Buy my book: https://www.lostincult.co.uk/howagamelives 

Social media and merch links at https://jacobgeller.com/

Watch my Nebula-Exclusive video on the book and movie “Holes”: https://nebula.tv/videos/jacob-geller-digging-deep-into-holes

Watch THIS video on Nebula: https://nebula.tv/videos/jacob-geller-a-video-about-digging-a-hole

Sources:
Amateur treasure hunter plunges 130 feet: https://nypost.com/2024/01/08/news/amateur-treasure-hunter-plunges-130ft-to-his-death-in-hole-he-dug-inside-his-home/
After 40 years' burrowing, Mole Man of Hackney is ordered to stop: https://www.theguardian.com/society/2006/aug/08/communities.uknews
The deepest hole we have ever dug: https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20190503-the-deepest-hole-we-have-ever-dug
The Kola superdeep borehole in action: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P4mzEGeMNAI&t=1200s
Kola Superdeep Borehole: https://www.atlasobscura.com/places/kola-superdeep-borehole?mc_cid=69025636df
At 2.8 km down, a 1-of-a-kind microorganism lives all alone: https://phys.org/news/2008-10-km-of-a-kind-microorganism.html


Media shown: A Game About Digging A Hole, Motherload, Minecraft, Holes, The Shawshank Redemption, The Core, Fantastic Mr. Fox, God of War II, Dragon’s Dogma II, 1000xRESIST, Neva, Echo Point Nova, Ed, Edd n Eddy, Cookie Clicker, PegIdle, Uzumaki

Music Used (Chronologically): Main Theme (SteamWorld Dig), New Heights in El Machino (SteamWorld Dig 2), Heavy Industry HQ (Motherload), Mergo’s Lullaby (Bloodborne), Ending (SteamWorld Dig), Human Resources (Perfect Vermin), Old World (SteamWorld Dig), The Rattlesnake (Holes), Dig It (Holes), Lorena 2 (Red Dead Redemption 2), Outlaws From the West (Red Dead Redemption 2), The Magnificent Four (Sunset Riders), The Sticks-for-Hands Rag (West of Loathing), Stage Clear (Sunset Riders), Ear to the Ground (Hanna Lindgren), Thorofare Hike (Firewatch), 

Additional music and sound effects from Epidemic Sound
Additional footage from Storyblocks and Getty Images

snippet.title: After Pope Francis, what happens next? | ABC NEWS
snippet.description:
Following the passing of Pope Francis, a strict set of rules and protocols is set into motion, guiding the transition to the next Pope. This tradition traces its origins back to Saint Peter—the first Pope—believed to have been chosen by Jesus himself. 
Subscribe: http://ab.co/1svxLVE
Read more here: https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-04-21/pope-francis-dies-catholic-church-vatican/103550594
Over the centuries, generations of Catholic leaders have refined the process into a meticulously choreographed and deeply internalized election. Ultimately, the Cardinals select one of their own to ascend as the moral and spiritual leader of the Catholic Church.

Lyrics:
Made a deal with the devil 
Put me down on my knees
 Like a cult or religion 
Trade my soul for a dream 
There’s no cure to my darkness 
Only perfect disease 
When my depression takes over 
You’re the one thing I need
Synthetic therapy 
If you want to see how I run right back to killing myself, taking my time 
Dancing with the devil in the pale moonlight 
At the end of every dream, there’s a demon saying I didn’t need help to ruin my life
Dancing with the devil in the pale moonlight 
Made a deal with the devil 
An apparition that bleeds 
What’s the price of your body
 If it is taken for free 
Yeah I was starved for attention 
But you can take it from me 
If there’s a hell underneath us That’s where you will find me 
Dance with the devil, Slave ‘til the end 
Beg for the dirt when they find you in a coffin

snippet.title: Let’s talk: Therapy, GLP1 & The Truth About My recent Weight Loss
snippet.description: This isn't easy to say, but I owe it to you to be honest. Janelle Rohner is micro dosing a GLP-1. I've quietly been working on my mental health, trying to find peace in the chaos. I know sharing this might open me up to judgment, but hiding it would mean losing the most important thing: my truth. I'm not perfect, but l'm healing-and I hope that means something to someone out there who's struggling too.

fr-FR.title: Parlons-en : thérapie, GLP1 et la vérité sur ma récente perte de poids
fr-FR.description: Ce n'est pas facile à dire, mais je vous le dois, pour être honnête. Janelle Rohner prend une microdose de GLP-1. Je travaille discrètement sur ma santé mentale, essayant de trouver la paix dans ce chaos. Je sais que partager cela pourrait m'exposer au jugement, mais le cacher signifierait perdre l'essentiel : ma vérité. Je ne suis pas parfaite, mais je guéris, et j'espère que cela aura un sens pour quelqu'un qui traverse également des difficultés.

ja.title: 話しましょう：セラピー、GLP1、そして最近の減量の真実
ja.description: 言いにくいことですが、正直に言う義務があります。ジャネル・ローナーはGLP-1をマイクロドーズしています。私はひっそりとメンタルヘルスに取り組んでいて、この混沌とし​​た状況の中で平穏を見つけようとしています。このことを話すと非難されるかもしれないことは分かっていますが、隠すことは最も大切なもの、つまり自分の真実を失うことを意味します。私は完璧ではありませんが、癒されつつあります。そして、同じように苦しんでいる誰かにとって、このことが少しでも意味のあることになれば嬉しいです。

hi.title: आइए बात करते हैं: थेरेपी, जीएलपी1 और मेरे हाल ही में हुए वजन घटाने के बारे में सच्चाई
hi.description: यह कहना आसान नहीं है, लेकिन ईमानदारी से कहूं तो मैं आपका आभारी हूं। जैनेल रोहनर जीएलपी-1 की माइक्रो डोज ले रही हैं। मैं चुपचाप अपने मानसिक स्वास्थ्य पर काम कर रही हूं, अराजकता में शांति खोजने की कोशिश कर रही हूं। मुझे पता है कि इसे साझा करने से शायद मुझ पर आलोचनाओं का दौर शुरू हो जाए, लेकिन इसे छिपाने का मतलब होगा सबसे महत्वपूर्ण चीज को खोना: मेरी सच्चाई। मैं परिपूर्ण नहीं हूं, लेकिन मैं ठीक हो रही हूं- और मुझे उम्मीद है कि इसका मतलब किसी ऐसे व्यक्ति के लिए भी होगा जो संघर्ष कर रहा है।

pt-BR.title: Vamos conversar: Terapia, GLP1 e a verdade sobre minha recente perda de peso
pt-BR.description: Não é fácil dizer isso, mas devo a vocês a honestidade. Janelle Rohner está microdosando um GLP-1. Tenho trabalhado discretamente na minha saúde mental, tentando encontrar paz em meio ao caos. Sei que compartilhar isso pode me expor a julgamentos, mas esconder significaria perder a coisa mais importante: a minha verdade. Não sou perfeita, mas estou me recuperando — e espero que isso signifique algo para alguém que também esteja passando por isso.

it.title: Parliamo: Terapia, GLP1 e la verità sulla mia recente perdita di peso
it.description: Non è facile dirlo, ma ti devo essere sincera. Janelle Rohner sta assumendo un microdosaggio di GLP-1. Ho lavorato in silenzio sulla mia salute mentale, cercando di trovare pace nel caos. So che condividere questo potrebbe espormi a giudizi, ma nasconderlo significherebbe perdere la cosa più importante: la mia verità. Non sono perfetta, ma sto guarendo, e spero che questo significhi qualcosa per qualcuno là fuori che sta lottando anche lui.

es-US.title: Hablemos: Terapia, GLP1 y la verdad sobre mi reciente pérdida de peso
es-US.description: No es fácil decirlo, pero te debo ser sincera. Janelle Rohner está tomando microdosis de GLP-1. He estado trabajando en mi salud mental en silencio, intentando encontrar paz en medio del caos. Sé que compartir esto podría exponerme a ser juzgada, pero ocultarlo significaría perder lo más importante: mi verdad. No soy perfecta, pero estoy sanando, y espero que esto le sirva de algo a alguien que también esté pasando por momentos difíciles.

de-DE.title: Reden wir: Therapie, GLP1 und die Wahrheit über meinen jüngsten Gewichtsverlust
de-DE.description: Das ist nicht leicht zu sagen, aber ich bin es dir schuldig, ehrlich zu sein. Janelle Rohner nimmt Mikrodosen von GLP-1. Ich habe still und leise an meiner psychischen Gesundheit gearbeitet und versucht, im Chaos Frieden zu finden. Ich weiß, dass ich mich durch das Teilen möglicherweise Verurteilungen aussetzen könnte, aber es zu verbergen würde bedeuten, das Wichtigste zu verlieren: meine Wahrheit. Ich bin nicht perfekt, aber ich bin auf dem Weg der Besserung – und ich hoffe, das bedeutet jemandem da draußen, der auch kämpft, etwas.

id.title: Yuk ngobrol: Terapi, GLP1 & Kebenaran Tentang Penurunan Berat Badan Saya Baru-baru Ini
id.description: Ini tidak mudah untuk dikatakan, tetapi jujur ​​saja, saya berutang budi kepada Anda. Janelle Rohner sedang mengonsumsi GLP-1 dalam dosis mikro. Saya diam-diam telah berusaha menjaga kesehatan mental saya, mencoba menemukan kedamaian di tengah kekacauan. Saya tahu bahwa berbagi ini mungkin akan membuat saya dihakimi, tetapi menyembunyikannya berarti kehilangan hal yang paling penting: kebenaran saya. Saya tidak sempurna, tetapi saya sedang dalam proses penyembuhan—dan saya harap itu berarti sesuatu bagi seseorang di luar sana yang juga sedang berjuang.

snippet.title: Loving Mother & Herd Do All They Can to Save Baby Buffalo from Lions
snippet.description:
When a hungry lion pride targeted a defenseless baby buffalo, things should have been over quickly. But, luckily, the very protective mother buffalo was still around and kept bashing the lions off her calf.
Not only that! The bravery of the mother buffalo gave the rest of the buffaloes the courage to come and join her rescue mission!

snippet.title: Ghost of Yōtei - The Onryō’s List | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Available on PS5® October 2, 2025.
Learn More: https://www.playstation.com/games/ghost-of-yotei/

Discover a bold, new story of a warrior in Japan who is on a mission of vengeance all her own.

Set 300 years after the critically acclaimed Ghost of Tsushima, Ghost of Yōtei is standalone experience set in 1600s rural Japan. The story follows a haunted, lone mercenary named Atsu. Thirsty for revenge, she travels through the beautiful, rugged landscapes of northern Japan, hunting those who killed her family many years earlier.

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/realfoltyn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered - Official Reveal
snippet.description:
The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered is here! Experience the beloved classic with a modern look and refined suite of features and updates.   

Bethesda Game Studios’ foundational open world role-playing game set the stage for nearly everything they have accomplished in the years since. Now Remastered, returning players and newcomers alike can experience the iconic RPG with a breathtaking new look. Get an in-depth look at all of the refinements in Oblivion Remastered, from visuals to gameplay and more.  

For more information about The Elder Scrolls, please visit https://elderscrolls.com or follow us on social media:

snippet.title: #6 TIMBERWOLVES at #3 LAKERS | FULL GAME 2 HIGHLGHTS | April 22, 2025
snippet.description:
The Lakers defeated the Timberwolves, 94-85 tonight in Los Angeles. Luka Dončić finished with a team-high 31 points along with 12 rebounds 9 assists and 2 three pointers for the Lakers, while LeBron James tallied 21 points, 11 rebounds and 7 assists in the game. Julius Randle recorded 27 points, 6 assists and 4 rebounds in the loss as Anthony Edwards added 25 points. The Lakers tie the series up at 1 game each.

snippet.description:

Chris Eubank Jr has failed to make the weight ahead of Saturday night's main event clash with Conor Benn 🚨

ja.description:

► Sky Sports Boxing に登録: http://bit.ly/SSBoxingSub

クリス・ユーバンク・ジュニアは、土曜夜のメインイベント、コナー・ベンとの対戦を前に、規定の体重を記録できなかった🚨

リング誌の報道によると、ユーバンクは最初の計量で160.2ポンド、2回目にして最後の計量で160.05ポンドを記録したという。報道によると、彼は50万ドル（37万5500ポンド）の罰金を科せられる予定で、土曜日の同日計量では体重が170ポンド（約80kg）を超えてはならず、超えた場合はさらに罰金が科せられるとのことです💰

snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls 4: Oblivion Remastered - 15 NEW Things You Need To Know Before You Buy
snippet.description:
Bethesda Softworks has finally announced what everyone has been buzzing about for weeks - The Elder Scrolls 4: Oblivion Remastered. Developed with Virtuos, the remaster features overhauled visuals made possible with Unreal Engine 5.

The character models, environments and other assets have been rebuilt from scratch. A new real-time lighting system allows for full dynamic shadows Cyrodiil, while the new lip-synching tech meshes well with the brand-new dialogue. Of course, there are also numerous quality-of-life improvements, from hit reactions in combat and an improved third-person perspective to sprinting and levelling changes.

The Elder Scrolls 4: Oblivion Remastered is out now on PS5, PC, and Xbox Series X/S for $49.99. You can also play it on Game Pass for PC, consoles, and the cloud, but here's what you should know before diving in.

snippet.title: I tried the 'Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion' Remaster...
snippet.description:
👉 All my links: https://linktr.ee/lukestephens 👈
-----------------------------------------------------------------
The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion™ Remastered modernizes the 2006 Game of the Year with all new stunning visuals and refined gameplay. Explore the vast landscape of Cyrodiil like never before and stop the forces of Oblivion from overtaking the land in one of the greatest RPGs ever from the award-winning Bethesda Game Studios.

Rediscover Cyrodiil
Journey through the rich world of Tamriel and battle across the planes of Oblivion where handcrafted details have been meticulously recreated to ensure each moment of exploration is awe-inspiring.

Navigate Your Own Story
From the noble warrior to the sinister assassin, wizened sorcerer, or scrappy blacksmith, forge your path and play the way you want.

Experience an Epic Adventure
Step inside a universe bursting with captivating stories and encounter an unforgettable cast of characters. Master swordcraft and wield powerful magic as you fight to save Tamriel from the Daedric invasion.

The Complete Story
Experience everything Oblivion has to offer with previously released story expansions Shivering Isles, Knights of the Nine, and additional downloadable content included in The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered.
~ Official Description

snippet.title: DOES IT SUCK? - Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered Review/Impressions! (PS5 Pro/Xbox)
snippet.description:
Like and subscribe if you enjoyed it!

Follow me on social media:
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/thedreamcastguy
BlueSky: https://bsky.app/profile/dreamcastguy.bsky.social
Instagram: http://instagram.com/dreamcastguy

The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion Remastered | Official Details

▫️ Rebuilt from the ground up in UE5 on top of Oblivion engine
▫️ Updated leveling system with some elements from Skyrim
▫️ Sprint added. Updated movement system.
▫️ New UI
▫️ Updated audio
▫️ Updated combat animations and gore
▫️ Recorded new lines of dialogue - each race now sounds unique
▫️ Includes all DLC expansions
▫️ Out now on PS5, PC, Xbox, and Xbox Game Pass

This is basically a remake!

Oblivion Remastered is quite literally a REMAKE.

Some major details:

- Gameplay touched up, new levelling system that's between Skyrim and Oblivion
- New voices added and new lines recorded
- All OG hilarious lines are back
- Fully remade visuals from the ground-up
- All animations remade
- Combat has been remade with a new dodge button
- You can now SPRINT!
- Unreal Engine 5 Visuals
- ALL DLCs are included

THIS IS AN INSANE PROJECT TO JUST SHADOWDROP, A HUGE DEA

snippet.title: Who could replace Pope Francis? Experts explain what could happen next
snippet.description: Following the death of Pope Francis, just hours after an Easter Sunday appearance, many are wondering who will be next. Any baptized Catholic male is eligible, though only cardinals have been selected since 1378. The winner must receive at least two-thirds of the vote from those cardinals under age 80 and thus eligible to participate.

snippet.title: Weapons | Teaser
snippet.description:
This is where the story really starts.
#WeaponsMovie 

From New Line Cinema and Zach Cregger, the wholly original mind behind Barbarian, comes a new
horror/thriller: Weapons.

When all but one child from the same class mysteriously vanish on the same night at exactly the
same time, a community is left questioning who or what is behind their disappearance.
The film stars Josh Brolin, Julia Garner, Alden Ehrenreich, Austin Abrams, Cary Christopher, with
Benedict Wong, and Amy Madigan.

Cregger directs from his own screenplay, and also produces alongside Roy Lee, Miri Yoon, J.D.
Lifshitz and Raphael Margules, with Michelle Morrissey and Josh Brolin executive producing. The
filmmaker’s creative team behind the camera includes director of photography Larkin Seiple, production
designer Tom Hammock, editor Joe Murphy and costume designer Trish Sommerville. The music is by
Ryan Holladay, Hays Holladay and Zach Cregger.

New Line Cinema Presents a Subconscious/Vertigo Entertainment/Boulderlight Pictures
Production, a Zach Cregger Film, Weapons. It will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures, and released in
theaters and IMAX nationwide on August 8, 2025, and internationally beginning in August 2025.

snippet.title: Cleetus Gets a Talladega Masterclass from Dale Jr.
snippet.description:
Dale Earnhardt Jr. teams up with Cleetus McFarland for an unforgettable walkthrough of Talladega Superspeedway — and it’s more than just a track tour. They dive into the intricacies of racing at Dega, from qualifying strategies and pit road entry to managing risk and understanding the unique layout. With Cleetus asking all the right questions, this convo is packed with insights for both new fans and seasoned diehards. As Cleetus gears up to run the ARCA race at Talladega, Dale Jr. shares valuable pointers to help him get up to speed. They also explore the infield and museum, uncovering historic race cars and vintage memorabilia that tell the story of NASCAR’s evolution. It’s a masterclass in what makes Talladega tick — from group qualifying dynamics to the importance of community, preparation, and learning from the best.

snippet.title: Original Movies in 2025: Oops, All Flops!
snippet.description: Movies, what have you done? The trend so far in 2025 is that any movie with a modest budget that’s not based on a recognizable property has been underperforming or flopping at the box office. Mike and Jay, seemingly with nothing better to do, have decided to look at the numbers and discuss this trend. What does the future of movies not based on video games and comic books look like? Does the long-established model of theatrical release need to change? Nobody knows and even less people care.

snippet.title: Major US retailers 'warn President Trump of empty shelves' if tariff policies continue | BBC News
snippet.description:
Walmart and Target, two of the biggest retailers in the US, have privately warned President Trump that their customers may face empty shelves in the coming weeks if his tariff policies continue, according to the BBC’s US partner CBS News.  

There’s evidence that the prohibitive level of tariffs imposed between China and the US are having a major impact on trade volumes.  Ports on the US west coast, in particular Los Angeles, are reporting a collapse in China  to US cargos, down 33% in the past week and expected to be down as much as 44% in the first week of May.

Walmart and Target are among the biggest retailers in the United States providing goods for millions of customers.  Both companies had already warned that the tariffs trade war could lead to higher prices. 

The Trump administration has levied 145% tariffs on Chinese goods and 10% tariffs on most other countries.  It has also imposed 25% tariffs on vehicle imports to the US.  It’s led to sharp falls in stock markets around the world along with fears of surging inflation and a slowdown in economic growth.

President Trump has said his tariff policies with reinvigorate US manufacturing.  He’s seeking to negotiate new trade deals and reach agreement with China, predicting that the current level of tariffs will come down significantly.

Jane Hill presents BBC News at Ten reporting from Faisal Islam in Washington.

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

For more news, analysis and features visit: www.bbc.com/news 

#BBCNews

snippet.title: Delta plane suffers engine fire in Florida forcing evacuation
snippet.description:
A Delta plane that caught on fire in Orlando on Monday caused passengers on board to evacuate.

Several people were seen getting off the plane as ambulances arrived at the tarmac.

Cellphone video showed the side of the plane on fire.

While details remain limited, the flight was headed to Atlanta from Orlando.

It's unclear what caused the fire.

snippet.title: ARGENTINA vs. BRASIL [4-1] | RESUMEN | ELIMINATORIAS SUDAMERICANAS | FECHA 14
snippet.description:
¡Goleada de #Argentina en el clásico! 👏🇦🇷

#EliminatoriasSudamericanas #Argentina 4 - 1 #Brasil 

El primer gol llegó ya a los 4’, De Paul inició la acción, la continuó Thiago Almada, que asistió con un pase entre líneas para la llegada por el centro de Álvarez, que le ganó a pura potencia a los centrales brasileño para definir entre las piernas de Bento.

La Albiceleste pareció tomar nota de las ganas de Brasil de igualar el encuentro y jugó una primera parte de alto nivel, en la que redujo a la Verdeamarelha, a partir de un juego dinámico, con mucho toque entre líneas, paciencia para controlar la pelota y claridad para atacar.

Así llegó el segundo tanto, una jugada en la que la Albiceleste tocó la pelota de un área a la otra, en la que sus once jugadores dieron pases durante más de un minuto y medio hasta que Nicolás Molina recibió por la derecha, envió el centro cruzado y Enzo Fernández entró a espaldas de la zaga visitante para estampar el 2-0 a los 12’.

Brasil no encontraba la llave para entrar en el partido, pero tuvo la suerte de un error del ‘Cuti’ Romero, quien falló en una salida y propició el descuento con un derechazo de Matheus Cunha a los 26’.

El equipo de Dorival insinuó un intento de ir por más, apareció Vinicius Júnior con un par de incursiones por la izquierda, pero Argentina asimiló bien el descuento y retomó el dominio, coronando un buen primer tiempo con el gol de Mac Allister para ampliar la ventaja a los 37’.

En la segunda parte llegó con el gol de Giuliano Simeone, que celebró su primer tanto con la Albiceleste tras un centro de Tagliafico a los 71’, apenas tres minutos después de ingresar.

En la próxima fecha, a jugarse en junio, Argentina visitará a Chile, mientras que Brasil acudirá a Ecuador.

snippet.title: Monster Hunter Wilds – Festival of Accord: Blossomdance | Spring Seasonal Event
snippet.description:
Bask in the springtime aura and enjoy cherry blossom season in the Grand Hub during the Festival of Accord: Blossomdance seasonal event, taking place in Monster Hunter Wilds for a limited time! Join the festivities to earn new free hunter and Palico layered armor, as well as a new Seikret decoration and more!
 
Event runs April 22 - May 6 PDT/ April 23 - May 7 BST.
